event_name: Prime Timers (Senior Adults): Antique Appraisal Show

event.description: Once again Jerry will join us to provide a free appraisal of an item of your choice. Jerry will appraise each item and give the history. The sooner he has information, the sooner he can start researching. Please email a photo, name and description of each item to elainethornlimb@gmail.com. Limited 1 item per person. Afterwords we will have pie, vanilla ice cream and fellowship. Please let Elaine know if you can bring a pie or have any questions at 971-275-2136.
